Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.84,0:00:34.81,Dial-CHI,Monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&B27DAB\4c&B27DAB\3a&88}我對幸福一無所知
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.81,0:00:37.06,Dial-CHI,Monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&B27DAB\4c&B27DAB\3a&88}些許希望
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.94,Dial-CHI,Monologue,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&B27DAB\4c&B27DAB\3a&88}也往往是過眼雲煙
